	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=36476><span id= >perrish</span></a><br><span id=notbold>102 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.85]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>If I want strength, it's so that I can carry stuff.&nbsp;&nbsp;VC plate legs have neg 0.5 to cargo capacity (str 6, wt 6.5).  And I can't wear them anyway.  Not everyone is a plate class, but even if they were, VC plate greaves are crap.  Neg agility, neg cargo capacity, one less ac.  No comparison.<br><br>These legs have plus 2 cargo capacity, and 14 ac.  For an all/all item, that's not crap.  Plus, for the folks who can wear leather or plate (so that the 14 ac isn't so impressive), there's the wis.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Necro 53 of Nighthaven<br>on Cazic-Thule</td></tr>
